

Packages : Contains one or more crates that provides a set of funtionality. Packages allows us to build , test and share crates.
    - Cargo.toml - Describe the package and define how to build crates
    - Rules
        - Must have a least 1 crate.
        - At most 1 binary crate.
        - Any number of binary crates.

Crates: A tree of  modules that produces a library or executable.

Modules: Lets you control the organisation and scope and privacy.
